    "English": "A living, fertile egg, <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">ready to hatch!</span><br><br>The creature inside wriggles its chubby limbs, patiently waiting to be hatched.<br><br>Scans indicate the being within has the genetic potential for a <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">loyal</span> personality.",
